    <item>
      <title>哈里斯的竞选搭档搜索锁定了三名主要竞争者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/kamala-harris-vice-presidential-search-focuses-on-3-candidates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯正在把注意力集中在一群潜在的竞选伙伴身上，她面临着为期两周的冲刺，以做出她即将举行的总统竞选中最重要的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/kamala-harris-vice-presidential-search-focuses-on-3-candidates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 15:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯放弃水力压裂禁令，共和党以过去立场为竞选纲领</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-backs-off-fracking-ban-as-gop-campaigns-on-past-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队表示，她不支持禁止水力压裂，这与她在 2019 年担任总统候选人时对热门油气开采技术的立场相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-backs-off-fracking-ban-as-gop-campaigns-on-past-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 14:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK Jr.) 宣称“比特币诺克斯堡” 特朗普被抢了风头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-gets-upstaged-by-rfk-jr-s-claims-of-bitcoin-fort-knox</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币社区一直在焦急地等待唐纳德·特朗普周六的讲话，但他的对手罗伯特·F·肯尼迪可能抢了特朗普的风头，他宣布，这位前总统正在考虑在他重返白宫后建立一个庞大的政府比特币储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-gets-upstaged-by-rfk-jr-s-claims-of-bitcoin-fort-knox</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 13:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班押注特朗普重返欧盟，增强其破坏者角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/orban-bets-on-trump-s-return-to-supercharge-role-as-eu-disruptor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班提出了新世界秩序的愿景，中国的支持和唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫，进一步放大了他在欧盟内部的叛徒角色。他甚至暗示了欧盟以外的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/orban-bets-on-trump-s-return-to-supercharge-role-as-eu-disruptor</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美寻求稳定，尽管争议海域局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/blinken-wang-see-importance-of-stability-in-us-china-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯和中国外交部长王毅在会晤中讨论了从台湾到南海紧张局势等安全问题，强调了两国之间保持稳定的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/blinken-wang-see-importance-of-stability-in-us-china-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 10:54:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
