      <title>法国铁路网络遭破坏后周一恢复正常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/paris-olympics-train-traffic-gradually-improving-after-sabotage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴黎奥运会开幕式前夕，法国铁路网络遭到未知身份人员的破坏，预计本周初法国铁路服务将恢复正常。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/paris-olympics-train-traffic-gradually-improving-after-sabotage</guid>
